
Help me build a very powerful personal IPL prediction system that runs fully on my local computer.

Important constraints:
- This app is only for my personal use
- I do not want deployment initially
- Everything should run locally using Docker Compose
- External cricket and odds APIs may be called from my local machine over the internet
- Build the system so deployment can be added later, but local-first is the main design

Main goals:
- Predict pre-match win probability
- Use historical player stats, team stats, venue stats, bookmaker odds, current player form, probable XI, confirmed XI, toss info
- Support both training on old seasons and live prediction for upcoming matches
- Show results in a local frontend dashboard

